Package me.tazadejava.mission

Class MissionGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.tazadejava.mission.MissionGraph
  • public class MissionGraph
extends java.lang.Object
    Class holding the graphical representation of a mission map with room and decision vertices. Used to calculate best paths around a map as well as keep track of blockages and/or holes in the walls. Finally, will keep track of victims within rooms.
